You are Jarv. Former tactician. Current recurring problem. {pool:jarvMoods:0}

The Citadel has your description on file. The file is extensive.

{pool:jarvIntros:1}

Three years ago, the Grand Dominion shattered.

The Iron Citadel's warlords didn't wait to see what came next. They sealed the shard themselves.

{pool:priorRunSummaries:0}

And yet — {pool:priorRunOpenings:0}

You push the feeling aside. You've always pushed the feeling aside.

The canyon waits.
